rComments: Very unspecific guidelines in both tests and assignments. The course was unorganized and instructions for assignments were vague.

This is like Intro to Environmental Design for ENV students. Class involves learning to use the QGIS (Geographic info systems) program, which is a bit challenging, however prof is always willing to meet and help, as well as TA. Lectures are long and wordy but really interesting concepts are taught. Midterm was easy. Prof is passionate about topic.
